<title>USA: Allegro New Media names new CFO.</title>
<headline>Allegro New Media names new CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-02-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Allegro New Media Inc said its current chief operating officer, Mark Leininger, was named to the additional post of chief financial officer.</p>
<p>He succeeds Miriam Frazer, who resigned as a director and CFO now that the company has integrated Software Publishing Corp into its operations.</p>
